1
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:08,380
Boss, you've been here for a while. Is everything okay?

2
00:00:08,380 --> 00:00:14,419
You're the one she's looking for.

3
00:00:14,419 --> 00:00:20,339
Do you remember what I did to return to the Arduan family?

4
00:00:20,339 --> 00:00:31,370
About Algar.

5
00:00:31,370 --> 00:00:37,619
Are you telling me that Mr. Arduan knows his illegitimate son is Algar?

6
00:00:37,619 --> 00:00:41,619
Yes, and now the old man wants him back.

7
00:00:41,619 --> 00:00:45,820
Mmm, another brat to show their inheritance.

8
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:48,820
If I could only get rid of his mother,

9
00:00:48,820 --> 00:00:51,820
getting rid of him shouldn't be a problem.

10
00:00:51,820 --> 00:00:53,820
Madam, it's our fault.

11
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:57,820
Please don't withdraw your donation to the orphanage.

12
00:00:57,820 --> 00:01:11,980
If we work together on this.

13
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:12,980
Take care of it.

14
00:01:12,980 --> 00:01:15,590
But make sure you're new to yourself.

15
00:01:15,590 --> 00:01:21,780
Yes, please.

16
00:01:21,780 --> 00:01:23,780
Have to see it, sir.

17
00:01:23,780 --> 00:01:30,579
I got rid of the woman who killed my mother.

18
00:01:30,579 --> 00:01:32,709
Sent me to an orphanage.

19
00:01:32,709 --> 00:01:40,000
Everyone associated with her over the years.

